money management podcasts.

116
00:04:29.596 --> 00:04:30.929
Where you gonna stay?

117
00:04:31.831 --> 00:04:33.394
-Oh. hell no. No.
-Please.

118
00:04:33.530 --> 00:04:35.066
Just put me in a little room.
No one will notice.

119
