Don't do it at the desk.

128
00:04:54.925 --> 00:04:56.361
Go to the bar. okay?
Jeff will help you. all right?

129
00:04:56.496 --> 00:04:57.520
-Okay. okay. okay. Love you.
-Love you. too.

130
