137
00:05:14.810 --> 00:05:17.212
No salt. just pepper.
And some fries.

138
00:05:17.347 --> 00:05:18.983
With a side of honey.

139
00:05:19.119 --> 00:05:20.611
Oh. and a beer. Any beer.

140
00:05:20.747 --> 00:05:21.912
