culinary school. but...

182
00:06:50.275 --> 00:06:51.541
Ah. you're a chef.

183
00:06:51.677 --> 00:06:53.772
No. no. no.
I never made it that far.

184
00:06:53.907 --> 00:06:55.237
(chuckles):
I dropped out

185
00:06:55.372 --> 00:06:57.712
